<br>
Yesterday I was in NE camp in PoV.  I had just gotten Agnarrs and had a Sapphire Bracelet on.  I was hitting in the 2400-2800 range with innate only crits in the 3800 area (no Crits AA for me yet).<br>
<br>
We picked up a 65th level bard who started playing Rizlona's Call of Flame and I did not notice my damage go up on either AT, ISoS or DoR. <br>
<br>
I was under the impression that they (the bracer and the song) are supposed to stack. I guess my question is:<br>
<br>
Are they supposed to stack? Because if they are, it ain't workin.<br>
<br>
